Popular Musician Kennedy Tarriq Ombima Aka King Kaka Announced Earlier Today That He Has Been Summoned By The Director Of Criminal Investigations Over His Controversial Song That Has Gripped The Attention Of The Country. This Comes As Kirinyaga Governor Anne Waiguru Threatened To Sue The Musician Accusing Him Of Occasioning Quote Irreparable And Permanent Damage To Her Reputation. Meanwhile Some Prominent Lawyers Have Offered Free Legal Services Should Governor Waiguru File A Suit.